e Sandai]]'' ||  || <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/010805/tv.html#5 |title='Me Mage Sandai' breaks all traditions |work=Sunday Times |accessdate=11 March 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2002 ||''[[Sathkampa]]'' || Benjamin || <ref name=\"Sarasaviya\">{{cite web |url=http://www.sarasaviya.lk/2015/10/08/?fn=sa15100828 |title=\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc4\u0dbd \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db1\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d91\u0daf\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dad \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0da0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db4\u0da7 |publisher=Sarasaviya |accessdate=11 March 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/021103/tv/1.html#1 | title='Sathkampa' tells of a woman's tragedy |work=Sunday Times| accessdate=29 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2002 ||''[[Arumosam Wahi]]'' ||  || <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/010805/tv.html |title='Arumosam Wehi' to storm Lankan cinema |work=Sunday Times |accessdate=27 November 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2002 ||''Mamath Geheniyak'' ||  || \n|-\n| 2003 ||''[[Thani Thatuwen Piyabanna]]'' || Doctor || <ref>{{cite web |url=https://gayasiafilms.wordpress.com/2015/05/21/flying-with-one-wing-3/ |title=FLYING WITH ONE WING |publisher=WordPress.com. |accessdate=11 March 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2003 || ''[[Sudu Kaluwara]]'' || Arachchi || <ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.island.lk/2003/07/19/satmag01.html | title=The Intruders (Sudu Kaluwara) - A cinematic spring of patriotism | publisher=The Island| accessdate=17 July 2019}}</ref> \n|-\n| 2004 ||''[[Mille Soya]]'' ||  || <ref>{{cite web |url=http://archives.dailynews.lk/2004/11/24/artscop14.html |title=Laudable exercise in free cinema concept|publisher=Daily News |accessdate=11 March 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2007 ||''[[Sankranthi (2007 film)|Sankranthi]]'' || Dr. Gerad || <ref>{{cite web|url= http://archives.sundayobserver.lk/2007/05/06/spe07.asp|title=Review: The Tender Trap (''Sankranthi'') Room for maturity|author=Indeewara Thilakarathne|date=6 May 2007|work=Sunday Obser